            "question": {
              "en": {
                "comprehension": null,
                "direction": null,
                "content": "<p>Indicate all correct alternatives, where base of the $\\log$ is 2 .</p>\n<p>The equation $x^{\\frac{3}{4}}\\left(\\log _2 x\\right)^2+\\log _2 x-\\frac{5}{4}=\\sqrt{2}$ has :</p>\n<p>(A) At least one real solution</p>\n<p>(B) Exactly 3 real solutions</p>\n<p>(C) Exactly one irrational solution</p>\n<p>(D) Imaginary roots</p>",
                "options": [
                  {
                    "identifier": "A",
                    "content": "A Only"
                  },
                  {
                    "identifier": "B",
                    "content": "A, B and D Only"
                  },
                  {
                    "identifier": "C",
                    "content": "A, B and C Only"
                  },
                  {
                    "identifier": "D",
                    "content": "B and D Only"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "hi": {
                "comprehension": null,
                "direction": null,
                "content": "<p>सभी सही विकल्पों को इंगित करें, जहाँ $\\log$ का आधार 2 है।</p>\n<p>समीकरण $x^{\\frac{3}{4}}\\left(\\log _2 x\\right)^2+\\log _2 x-\\frac{5}{4}=\\sqrt{2}$ के हैं :</p>\n<p>(A) कम से कम एक वास्तविक हल</p>\n<p>(B) ठीक 3 वास्तविक हल</p>\n<p>(C) ठीक एक अपरिमेय हल</p>\n<p>(D) काल्पनिक मूल</p>",
                "options": [
                  {
                    "identifier": "A",
                    "content": "केवल A"
                  },
                  {
                    "identifier": "B",
                    "content": "केवल A, B और D"
                  },
                  {
                    "identifier": "C",
                    "content": "केवल A, B और C"
                  },
                  {
                    "identifier": "D",
                    "content": "केवल B और D"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "subTopic": null,
            "subject": "mathematics",
            "timeAllotted": 90000,
            "topic": "logarithmic-equations",
            "type": "mcq"
          },
